Show HN: AI-powered Chrome ext. for generating high-quality replies on Twitter
text: Are you tired of struggling to come up with the perfect response to tweets? Look no further than TweetSpear, the new chrome extension that uses artificial intelligence to generate effective and engaging replies. Simply select the tweet you want to respond to, and TweetSpear will provide you with a selection of thoughtfully crafted responses to choose from. Sign up for the waitlist now at https://tweetspear.com and revolutionize the way you tweet.

title: Skype on phone/androind asking permission access your phone refusing WiFi call?
text: Is Skype on phone/androind asking permission access your phone for spying on you? (i.e. skype does not need to access phone as it should be only optional as it used to work, but since recently MS has decided to not allow skype call over WiFi or cellular data if you do not allow them to spy on you!! Skype before, and other apps like Viber do not do this and I see this as MS draconianism and greed.)
